OL,4,G0255FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe competition kicks off at
OL,6,     GAbbey House in Penrith, Cumbria,
OL,7,     Gwhere Ian Sugden and his wife Sam
OL,8,     Gtreat their guests to an
OL,9,     Gafternoon on the firing range and
OL,10,     Gfancy bacon for breakfast.
OL,11,G0325FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GLisa Holloway prides herself on
OL,13,     Gproviding a home from home at
OL,14,     GCompton House in Newark,
OL,15,     GNottinghamshire. But there are
OL,16,     Gdusty discoveries, and Dave and
OL,17,     GJo find the prices hard to
OL,18,     Gswallow.
