OL,4,G0445FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers meet for one last time
OL,6,     Gto settle some scores and find
OL,7,     Gout how much they've been paid. A
OL,8,     Gheated exchange about cleaning
OL,9,     Gleads to tears before the winner
OL,10,     Gis announced.
OL,11,G0515FCouples Come Dine with Me
OL,12,     GIn West Yorkshire, there are
OL,13,     Gterrible jokes, comedy teeth,
OL,14,     Gplate licking and a conga, as
OL,15,     Gthree couples compete to host the
OL,16,     Gbest dinner party.
